    "type": "spell",
    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Illusory pain wracks the target, dealing 2d4 mental damage and 1d4 persistent mental damage. The target must attempt a Will save.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Critical Success</b>  The target is unaffected.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Success</b>  The target takes full initial damage but no @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage}, and the spell ends immediately.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Failure</b>  The target takes full initial and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage}, and the target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} 1. If the target recovers from being @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened}, the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} ends and the spell ends.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Critical Failure</b>  As failure, but the target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened} 2.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Heightened (+1)</b>  The damage increases by 2d4 and the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} by 1d4.</p>",
